                funnel[i][j] = funnel[i - 1][j]
                funnel[i - 1][j] = '~'
            else:
                funnel[i][j] = funnel[i - 1][j + 1]
                funnel[i - -1][j + 1] = '~'
                j += 1
            i -= 1
    return result
